(6631, 2105, 'questions_0_question', 'How do I make a personalized book? '),
(6632, 2105, '_questions_0_question', 'field_62423f8a3dc8a'),
(6633, 2105, 'questions_0_answer', 'Browse our collection of book topics and select the one that best matches the upcoming event/change. Complete a short questionnaire and upload photographs to customize your child’s change story. We’ll weave everything together into a unique photo storybook, which you can preview before you buy. Your print book will arrive at your doorstep in 7 to 10 business days.'),
(6634, 2105, '_questions_0_answer', 'field_62423f943dc8b'),
(6635, 2105, 'questions_1_question', 'How much does an Up & Coming book cost?  '),
(6636, 2105, '_questions_1_question', 'field_62423f8a3dc8a'),
(6637, 2105, 'questions_1_answer', 'Each custom photo storybook is $30. We offer two different shipping options, standard and speedy – speedy is ideal if you need a story in a hurry. '),
(6638, 2105, '_questions_1_answer', 'field_62423f943dc8b'),
(6639, 2105, 'questions_2_question', 'How will an Up & Coming personalized photo storybook help my child through a transition?'),
(6640, 2105, '_questions_2_question', 'field_62423f8a3dc8a'),
(6641, 2105, 'questions_2_answer', 'Help your child anticipate the joys and challenges of new experiences in their very own life with a customized photo story book. Help your child anticipate the joys and challenges of new experiences in their very own life with a customized photo story book.'),
